COMIS Reference table (which is used by the Drug Product Reference File to generate Approved Drug Products with Therapeutic Equivalence Evaluations (a.k.a. The Orange Book)), and the Drug Registration and Listing Database, Office of Epidemiology and Biosurveillance Database.
